            span.sidebar__days__single-day__meetup__title
              | TC Talks SP

        .sidebar__days__single-day
          .sidebar__days__single-day__header
            h3.sidebar__days_monday__title
              | 13/7 - Sexta
          a.sidebar__days__single-day__meetup(href='https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/Frontend-Dev-SP-Meetup/events/251780679/', target='_blank', rel='noopener')
            .sidebar__days__single-day__meetup__color.sidebar__days__single-day__meetup__color_Frontend-SP
            span.sidebar__days__single-day__meetup__title
              | Frontend SP

